dct_title_s: Insurance maps of New Jersey coast, New Jersey, volume four (Sheet 101)
dct_description_sm: Includes Avalon, Cape May City, Cape May Point, Five Mile Beach, Grassy Sound, Lower Township, North Wildwood, Ocean City, Sea Isle City, South Cape May, Stone Harbor, Strathmere, West Cape May, West Wildwood, Wildwood, and Wildwood Crest. "New index, April, 1937": preliminary sheets 1-2. Key map on preliminary sheet 3. Includes key, key map, index, and text. "9120."
dct_publisher_sm: New York : Sanborn Map Company, 1937, c1909.
dct_subject_sm: Fire insurance maps—New Jersey—Cape May County—1937
dcat_theme_sm: Fire insurance maps—New Jersey—Cape May County—1937
